{
  "id": "adv_card_rui_08_01",
  "title": "天動瑠依 1話 私一人だけですか？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――とある音楽番組の収録後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After a music program recording.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1699.9999324999999,
          "startTime": 1.6999999325
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。今日の収録、凄く良かったよ\nトリエルは安定感があるから安心して見ていられるな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work. Today’s recording was great.\nTRINITYAiLE is so stable‚ it’s reassuring to watch.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.7333333254,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.5203623176
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます\n安定感があると評価していただけるのは嬉しいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you so much.\nI’m glad you think our performance is stable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.2999999921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "常にベストなパフォーマンスが出来るように\n心がけて、日々練習をしていますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To deliver the best performance in any situations‚\nI strive to practice every day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.1333333254,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.5852148414
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "練習に裏打ちされた自信か……瑠依らしいな\n瑠依は昔からそんな風に堂々としていたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Confidence backed by practice… That’s so like you‚ Rui.\nHave you always been so confident?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.9999999921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "私だって\n最初からなんでもうまく出来た訳じゃありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not really.\nI wasn’t good at everything from the beginning.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.9333333254,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.3853257696
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "デビュー当時は気負って空回りして\n失敗することもよくありました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I first debuted‚ I was so eager that I often made mistakes‚\nand even failed many times.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.1999977033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依が空回りする姿なんて想像もつかないが……\n一体どんな失敗をしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t imagine you making mistakes…\nWhat kind of mistakes did you make?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.6999994834,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.1506766835
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "それは……\n恥ずかしいので言いたくありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well…\nIt’s embarrassing‚ so I don’t want to say.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.4666661501,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.3585022806
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "頑張った結果なら、何も恥ずかしがることは\nないと思うが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's the result of your hard work‚ so I think\nyou don't have to be embarrassed…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.1333353599,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "私だって見栄を張りたい時もあります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sometimes‚ I want to look good too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.7874365527,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.1667355895
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "特に{user}さんにだけは……\n恥ずかしい姿を知られたくありません……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Especially in front of you…\nI don't want you to see my embarrassing side…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.6666707278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.1141050696
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "と、とにかく、昔の私は実力も経験も不足していて\n全力でぶつかることしか出来なかったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A…anyway‚ back then‚ I lacked both skill and experience‚\nso all I could do was give it my all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.6000020266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.6888216694
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "でも、そういうがむしゃらな姿勢がいいと\n褒めてくれる人もいて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ some people liked that reckless side of me\nand complimented me for it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.9000020266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "初めて出演した音楽番組も、MCの方がトリエルの\n姿勢を気に入って番組に推してくれたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "On the first music program I appeared on‚ the MC liked TRINITYAiLE’s attitude\nand recommended us to the program.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.2000020266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.2999551177
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "推したくなる気持ちは俺も分かるよ\n頑張っている瑠依達を見ていると応援したくなるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand why he would recommend you.\nWatching your hard work makes me want to support you‚ Rui.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.4666686933,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "私は自分に出来ることを精一杯しているだけですが……\nそんな風に思ってもらえるのはありがたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm just doing my best with what I can do…\nbut I'm grateful that you think so.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.2333353599,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.792653819
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルは沢山の人に助けられてここまで来ました\nお世話になった人達には、いつか恩返ししたいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "TRINITYAiLE has come this far thanks to the help of many people.\nI hope we can repay those who have helped us someday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.6333353599,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.8545130135
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "お世話になった人達と言えば……バンプロにいた頃に\n何度か出演した三十分枠の音楽番組を覚えてるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of those who have helped us… Do you remember that 30-minute music program\nwe appeared on a few times when I was in Van Prods.?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.4666686933,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "関東ローカルの小さな番組ですよね？　もちろんです\nそれが、さっき話した初めて出演した音楽番組です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That small‚ local program in the Kanto region? Of course I do.\nThat’s the first music program I mentioned.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.9000020266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったのか……\nその番組だが、終了することが決定したそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…\nI heard that program has been decided to end.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.2333353599,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.1479379376
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですか！？　思い入れがある番組なので\n終わってしまうのは寂しいですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really?! It’s a program that holds a special place in my heart‚\nso it’s sad to hear that it’s ending…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.2999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.4401146294
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "それで、最終回はぜひトリエルに出演してほしいと\nオファーを受けたんだが、どうする？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ they sent me an offer for TRINITYAiLE to appear\non the final episode‚ what do you think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.1356937011,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 151.0353529336
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん出ます！\n最終回のゲストに指名してもらえるなんて光栄です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course we’ll do it!\nIt’s an honor to be nominated as guests for the final episode.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.6356937011,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.9250126562
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-rui016.m4a",
